<HEADLINE>
DUCKS BEAT STARS
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
(OPTIONAL: Adds quotes, details) 
By GREG CHRISTENSEN  
 San Gabriel Valley Tribune  
<TEXT>
