<HEADLINE>
EXTRA-WITTY! THEY'VE GONE OVER-BARD 
</HEADLINE>
  (The Week in Review) 
(NOTE TO INTERNATIONAL CLIENTS: For use by special arrangement
only. Asian and European points: Call Karl Horwitz in Paris for
details and prices, phone: 47 42 17 11; fax: 47-42-80-44). Latin
American points: Call Olivia Vasquez in Los Angeles, phone:
310-996-0075; fax: 310-996-0089). 
(lb) 
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
<P>
   How have the media been recycling Shakespeare lately in the
midst of the playwright's pop-culture renaissance? Let us only
begin to count the ways with the following headlines, starting with
last week's Oscar awards, at which ``Shakespeare in Love'' won Best
Picture.
