<DOCNO> NYT19990327.0087 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-03-27 14:10 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1652 &Cx1f; var-z
u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-NY-POLICE-PROTESTS-RE     03-27 1135
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-NY-POLICE-PROTESTS-REVIEW-425&AMP;ADD-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
CIVIL DISOBEDIENCE, NEGOTIATED 
</HEADLINE>
  (The Week in Review) 
(NOTE TO INTERNATIONAL CLIENTS: For use by special arrangement
only. Asian and European points: Call Karl Horwitz in Paris for
details and prices, phone: 47 42 17 11; fax: 47-42-80-44). Latin
American points: Call Olivia Vasquez in Los Angeles, phone:
310-996-0075; fax: 310-996-0089). 
(lb) 
