contact Stewart Slavin at the Daily News, (818) 713-3701.
</P>
<P>
   FREEWAY-MISTAKE (Los Angeles) _ Thousands of L.A. drivers pay
every day for a mistake the state transportation agency made 32
years ago _ the failure to connect the 5 and 134 freeways in all
four directions. By Lee Condon. (Will move in the ``n'' California
news file and ``a'' national news file.)
</P>
