<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-03-27 19:28 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6645 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u i &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-KOSOVO-MAIN-BOS &LR;      03-27 1242
